summary: An ordinance relating to the construction of a watermain on Juneau Street, from Beacon Avenue to 51st Avenue South; a watermain on 5th Avenue Southwest, from the West Seattle Reservoir to West Kenyon Street; a watermain on 49th Avenue Southwest, from West Juneau Street to Canada Drive, and other streets; a concrete dam on Cedar River; and the removal of surface soil at Lake Youngs, and amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 63736.
